comment.undefined: The WINGS Execution is a WINGS workflow class that represents the execution of a WINGS Workflow template specification.
The WINGS ExecutionStep is a WINGS workflow class that represents the execution step (process) of a WINGS Workflow template specification.
The WINGS hasRunId is a WINGS workflow data property that represents a WingsWorkflowExecution having an runID for its current run.
The WINGS hasStep is a WINGS workflow object property that represents a connection between a WingsWorkflowExecution having an execution step.
The WINGS hasEndTime is a WINGS workflow data property that represents a WingsWorkflowExecution having an endTime for its execution.
The WINGS hasPlan is a WINGS workflow object property that represents a connection between a WingsWorkflowExecution having an Workflow Instance.
The WINGS hasStartTime is a WINGS workflow data property that represents a WingsWorkflowExecution having an startTime for its execution.
The WINGS hasExecutionStatus is a WINGS workflow data property that represents a WingsWorkflowExecution having a status for its execution that was currently active.
The WINGS hasExpandedTemplate is a WINGS workflow object property that represents a connection between a WingsWorkflowExecution having an WingsWorkflowExpandedTemplate.
The WINGS hasTemplate is a WINGS workflow object property that represents a connection between a WingsWorkflowExecution having a template.
